Description

For piano.

T.p. ill.: title and composer statement surrounded by lithograph drawings of gothic (revival?) arches.

Extract from "La France musicale" by Gustave Choquet, explaining the genesis of this composition, printed on page [2].

Multiple copyrights by various entities listed at the bottom of p. 3.

Copy 1: "L.M. Gottschalk." (publisher's listing)--P. [1] recto of brown wrapper.

Copy 1: "Choice compositions for pianoforte practice." (publisher's listing)--P. [2] verso of brown wrapper.

Copy 1 covered by brown wrapper with publisher's listings on the front and back covers.
